I can think of.

436
00:20:15,860 --> 00:20:18,570
<i> I wanted to do</i>
<i> the team Merrill deployment.</i>

437
00:20:18,670 --> 00:20:23,170
<i> I wanted the, the action.</i>
<i> I wanted to test myself.</i>

438
00:20:23,270 --> 00:20:25,240
I'm not the strongest,
I'm not the fastest or anything,

439
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:28,080
but I'll just keep putting
one foot in front of the other.

440
00:20:28,180 --> 00:20:30,880
Can't make me quit, so.

441
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:36,750
As snipers, we were in charge
of navigating,

