00:20:41,790 --> 00:20:43,920
<i> So basically</i>
<i> we ended up walking</i>

445
00:20:44,030 --> 00:20:46,260
<i> a very rudimentary dirt road</i>

446
00:20:46,360 --> 00:20:48,530
with brush and weeds and,
